high_descs: Walk forward and make a left around the counter to face the middle of it.
Pick up the white plate from the middle of the counter.
Make a left to walk to the microwave.
Heat up the white plate in the microwave, removing it afterwards.
Turn right to walk to the sink.
Set the white plate down to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Microwave the white plate to set it down by the sink.

high_descs: Put the plate in the microwave and heat it.
Get the plate back and walk over to the sink
Place the plate on the counter
anns.task_desc: Heat a plate up and put it on the counter

high_descs: Walk forward, then turn left at the end of the bar and turn to face the bar.
Pick up the white platter closest to you on the bar.
Turn left and walk to the end of the bar, then turn left again and walk to the stove on the right.
Put the platter in the microwave over the stove and turn it on to warm it, then take the platter out.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the platter on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm platter on the counter to the left of the sink.
